      "content": "Wait, what do you mean by \"ancient gnomes\" and \"goblin's pointed nose\"? I'm just trying to learn the engineering mechanics for my exam. Can you just stick to the technical explanation of how the pressure differential works and finish what you were saying about the blockages?",
